Events & Workshops

Git Set Go!

11 March at 5:00 PM

Sri Kadimisetty, Senior

Git is a distributed version control system. It is one skill every software professional is bound to run into in their career. We use it here to run our website and do other cool stuff. You will learn how to manage your projects better with Git be introduced to the popular code sharing website github.com. Participants also get a tiny surprise gift.
